TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Singularity of the Information Matrix of the Mixed Proportional Hazard Model
AU  - Ridder, Geert
AU  - Woutersen, Tiemen M.
AB  - [This paper presents new identification conditions for the mixed proportional hazard model. In particular, the baseline hazard is assumed to be bounded away from 0 and ∞ near t = 0. These conditions ensure that the information matrix is nonsingular. The paper also presents an estimator for the mixed proportional hazard model that converges at rate N<sup>-1/2</sup>.]
